Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, you went to a school in the middle of the city, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You, a hikikomori, actually went to a place with lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's big progress, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I'm impressed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I might as well say that my hikikomori condition has been cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you should be fine going outside by yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I'm not hikikomori anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:18.72,Note,,0,0,0,,Kokogi Designer Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
