Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HA49E96&\fs36.303\frx350\fry12\frz17.027\pos(972.584,387.227)}Conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the project is due today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I got it right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your work is pretty amateurish actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Is it a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eject!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was them behind this all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the victim of a conspiracy plotted by the Nihon Hikikomori Kyokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,St-Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have you do this every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you've been paying for my services.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,People always say that summer colds take a long time to get over,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but you really have been sick for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, my body still feels sluggish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought your hikikomori condition got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, I went to your school the other day by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a big liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a conspiracy plotted by the Nihon Hikikomori Kyokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I visited Yamazaki's school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,my hikikomori condition has gotten much worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want to answer my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to even live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But dying is a pain in the ass too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what would have happened to me if Yamazaki had never come to check on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just lied to Yamazaki saying I had a summer cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure he's going to find out that's a lie sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight, Sato! Fight against the enemy's conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Our common enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You must fight against the conspiracy plotted by the Nihon Hikikomori Kyokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight against them? But I don't have any weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Love and courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have love or courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.24,Background2,,0,0,0,,A phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is certainly unusual. Telephone's calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:13.56,Background2,,0,0,0,,A phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's been some kind of accident or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.24,Background2,,0,0,0,,A phone call! A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Telephone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.26,Background2,,0,0,0,,A phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:35.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fscx50\fscy38.75\org(746,264)\frx18\fry14\frz23.69\pos(750,257.5)\c&H1D7297&\3c&H7AE2FF&\4c&H7BE2FF&}RECORDING...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm not available to take your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to send me a fax, please press your send button now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? It's Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some business in Tokyo, so I'm coming up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking I should drop by and see you while I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And we could discuss your future plans and stuff then too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.46,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.852\fscx78.333\fscy63.75\c&H1D7297&\3c&H7BE2FF&\4c&H7BE2FF&\pos(438.651,323.698)\fax-0.07}RECORDING...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's coming here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Discuss my future plans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she planning to make me move back home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a freakin' break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything I've done to move to Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just be a loser if I move back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro? Oh, you're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I answered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're home, answer the phone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just came back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then I guess you still haven't checked your message,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but my class reunion is coming up on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days from today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like I'll have some free time the day before the reunion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want to see you and discuss some things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Two days from today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just keep on wasting your time doing nothing in Tokyo forever, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it time for you to come back home and get a job down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides you'll never be able to get married at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm fine, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've already found a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a small software company, but I've been writing scripts and stuff for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't told you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's someone I'm considering getting married to as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I've pretty much decided on settling down here in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good for you, Tatsuhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But good, you've got a job now and you're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the marriage part isn't gonna happen anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they don't pay you a whole lot when you start a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right! Just knowing that you've got a girlfriend is such a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to let me meet her when I come to Tokyo, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll call you again with the flight information and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:06.71,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz41.49\frx354\fry24\pos(1096.666,127.5)\c&H1D7297&\3c&H7BE2FF&\4c&H7BE2FF&}IN USE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't buy into it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell it's a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Software company... script writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, be more suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Err, it's not Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Mr. Tatsuhiro Sato's residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the right number then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've been worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't shown up for counseling or answered your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Misaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One million yen penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I have a really good reason for this whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I have a more important thing to worry about right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just found out that my mother is coming to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you told her you've got a job at a promising company
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and a girlfriend who's going to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are limits to how much you should make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She was planning to drag me back home unless I told her stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two more days before she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to come up with a way to fool her before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A company and a girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice, do I, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind pretending to be your girlfriend for a day if you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, there's Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to ask Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya-Yamazaki is going to be your girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no time to waste! I'm gonna ask Yamazaki right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki! Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A company! We're gonna make a company, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you can establish a company with as little as one yen capital these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If we establish a company, I can fool my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, we were gonna make the world's preeminent game company to begin with anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that our plan has been accelerated a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're are going to proudly bring our own brand to the game industry, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Our brand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds great! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\fscx251.667\fscy202.5\b1\pos(650,287.5)}LET'S MAKE A COMPANY!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx221.667\fscy183.75\pos(626.666,372.5)}LET'S PICK A COMPANY NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pick a company name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's pick a company name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take "Sa" from Sato and '"Yama" from Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and call it "Sayama Company"! How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But then it sounds like a person named Sayama founded the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about something non-Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't memorize all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.85,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx215\fscy175\pos(640,370)}LET'S MAKE A COMPANY LOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a company logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, for now let's say that our company name is '"Y.S. Company."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not happy with the name either, so let's change it once we become big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is the company logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's "Y.S.", how about something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it looks like a logo on the baseball cap for some baseball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, for now, just for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:14.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx161.667\fscy157.5\pos(636.666,357.5)}LET'S MAKE A COMPANY SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a company song!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Company song! Company song! Company song for Y.S.!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:20.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx171.667\fscy156.25\pos(633.334,360)}LET'S MAKE BUSINESS CARDS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make business cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:25.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}President: Kaoru Yamazaki\NY.S. Company Limited
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,President, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to call myself "co-president,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've already told my mother that I found a job, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a job title that's perfect for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:38.77,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}NEET: Tatsuhiro Sato\NY.S. Company Limited
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,NEET?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains your current status in on simple word, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working hard so that she doesn't find out that's what I am, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, NEET isn't a business title!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:51.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H000002&\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx166.667\fscy161.25\pos(630,357.5)}LET'S MAKE A RECEPTION DESK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a reception desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The reception desk is the face of the company!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we're going to ask her to be the receptionist for our company!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:13:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\c&H000000&\shad0\bord3.781\frz37.087\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(562.696,334.286)}Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord3.781\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscx93.333\fscy82.5\frz39.237\pos(864.719,400.84)\fax-0.1}Reception Desk
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now our company is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to show this to your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, at the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what we need is for it to appear as though our company is legit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't really want to bring her to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:28.40,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Tatsuhiro Sato\NY.S. Company Limited
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she'll be convinced if I show this business card to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to fool her about the girlfriend who's going to marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot about that problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to, I can pretend to be your girlfriend for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\fs33.278\frz26.969\pos(447.64,190.589)}Kashiwa Hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Senpai will help me out on this one if I explain the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's possible that something intended as a lie could come true too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Senpai? It's Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I already have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have an appointment with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My only hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, I guess I'll have Yamazaki dress in drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Mother! I'm Kaoru Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it for you, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,play your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, do we really have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, when you lie, it's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't have at least one real date beforehand, she'll be able to tell you're lying right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I go to some place with a bunch of people, the same thing might happen to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're together, I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is what a so-called "normal relationship" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've made it more official and dated each other back then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try walking arm in arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We look more like a real couple that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll look normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that I'm feeling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be the sign?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she coming on to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this lie turning into the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time will be the real deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better clean up your apartment, or your mother will be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to pretend to be a couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,won't it be a problem if we don't know more about each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is about the only thing I know about you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I know you very well, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Name, Tatsuhiro Sato. Date of birth, January 28th, Aquarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood type A. You were born in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hobby is watching videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and recently you've gotten into gal games and collecting pictures of a "graphic" nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The last place you attended school was at Heisei Bunka University, a private school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but you dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father's name is Tatsuo. Mother's name is Shizue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you know so much about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have a good memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Mr. Tatsuhiro Sato's residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she knows the phone number to my apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The only people I've given that number to are my parents back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't told me anything about yourself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a problem if I don't know anything about you when my mother asks me, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll tell you, but you have to memorize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll tell you about my family tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather is French and his name is Georges Brufelles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother is a Japanese prima donna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They met at Port Moresby and fell in love. They came back to Japan and got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my mother was born and she got married to my father, an elite businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I was born, but now I live with my relatives due to unavoidable familial circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is my grandfather's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,John... Brook... Brooklyn?
