Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,George Bl... No, Bly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's obviously a lie! What does she mean, he's French?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who is she?
